<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>cross over Jordan • cross the Rubicon</xh5><p> <i>cross over Jordan</i>—(also: cross over to the other side) die; pass away: Following a stroke which left her comatose, she <u>crossed over Jordan</u> on February 3, 1972, and is buried at Laurel Land Cemetery.</p><p><i>cross the Rubicon—</i>take an irrevocable step; make a fateful and final decision: Now is the time for Koizumi to <u>cross the Rubicon</u> and take decisive action to implement the radical structural reforms.</p> </entry>
